## Table
you can show data by table.

Table = <table>
Row = <tr>
Header = <th>  //it will give bold text
Data = <td>

example:

<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Age</th>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Hemel</td>
    <td>22</td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Bhai</td>
    <td>24</td>
  </tr>
</table>

^^ Caption:
you can add table capion by this
<caption> your caption</caption>


^^ Table head and Table body:
you can use it for structure.
its not visible in font but in inspect its visible.

syntex:

<thead>
your table header
</thead>


<tbody>
your all table data
<tbody>

^^ Callspan"
its use for one header for many data

syntex:
<th callspan="how much you want">
your header
<th>

